			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The crushbone belts can be given to a guy in the warrior's guild in Kaladim.  Anyone can do this, and the reward is a gold or two and a random piece<BR>
of tattered armor per belt.  In mass quantities, this pays off.  I had 50 belts in backpacks in the bank, and after selling the armor, gained about <BR>
6-7 platinum.  The same guy also accepts lego shoulderpads for an even better reward.  I believe his name is Conloe Nusbuk ( or something similar ).
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
