			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				You get the belts by killing orc centurions in Crushbone...not the ones outside the zone.  The shoulder pads you get off of the legionnaires. They offer lousy AC protection so use them for the quest or sell.  EQ now has the merchants selling them for 6-7 pp each so it is no longer worthwhile buying them from the merchants and makes it much more profitable to sell them.<BR>
<BR>
I have sold mine for 1-2 pp each and at a level 19 druid, I just walk into CB and cast 1 shot of my 94 damage spell to kill a centurion and hopefully get a belt to sell.
				</font>
